de.tlabs.mobileCloud.benchmarkBundle2
Class fasta

java.lang.Object
  de.tlabs.mobileCloud.benchmarkBundle2.fasta

 class fasta
extends java.lang.Object

Each program should encode the expected cumulative probabilities for 2 alphabets generate DNA sequences, by weighted random selection from the alphabets, using this linear congruential generator IM = 139968 IA = 3877 IC = 29573 Seed = 42 Random (Max) Seed = (Seed * IA + IC) modulo IM = Max * Seed / IM generate DNA sequences, by copying from a given sequence write 3 sequences line-by-line in FASTA format Modified for PowerDroid framework by Andrius Aucinas

Author:
Andrius
